item.title: Necoyoad
item.description:
Necotienda

I re-designed and re-wrote the e-commerce front-end and its many default plugins. Most of the improvement of resolve around:

  • The overall UI/UX;
  • Better code quality and integrated development tools.
  • Improvement and bugs catching on the default plugins.
  • Faster page loads and dependency management.
  • Better feedback and improvements on accessibility.

item.title: about
item.description:
My name is Jesús and I am originally from Venezuela. I am frontend web developer with more than 3 years of experience and highly skilled in web front-end technologies. I can develop fast, responsive, high quality & user friendly clients with your goals in mind.

Most of my experience resolve around working with e-commerce platform, developing dashboards for web apps and JavaScript plugins.
